  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique game mechanics</h2>Players can change gravity to explore the level.While changing the gravity, the player will also change the colour. Characters of the same colour can only stand on the corresponding platform.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=584 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse ways to play</h2>There is a variety of methods to play the game. The game has more than eighty levels and 6 chapters, with each chapters encompassing different rules and hurdles. Players will be able to enjoy and tackle the arrays of challenges set up in each chapter <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet your past self</h2>If you could go back in time and see your younger self, what would you have said to her? In the midst of chaos, the grown-up protagonist has met her past self. The two must work together to escape this time space<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility Settings</h2>Blind players can also play \"Red&Black\"! ! !<br>Through the game's accessibility settings, blin can also enjoy the fun of solving puzzles and action games.<br>This mode needs to start NVDA or call the NVDA interface for experience.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/5219f068be8dfd4b3f1b931ff79f42b3.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique game mechanics</h2>Players can change gravity to explore the level.While changing the gravity, the player will also change the colour. Characters of the same colour can only stand on the corresponding platform.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=584 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/0a7de0fcdbae2a362a92590eaee94c14.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse ways to play</h2>There is a variety of methods to play the game. The game has more than eighty levels and 6 chapters, with each chapters encompassing different rules and hurdles. Players will be able to enjoy and tackle the arrays of challenges set up in each chapter <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.poster.avif?t=1684147181\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.webm?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365780/extras/db6b893370ca8ef3c7506749422f7978.mp4?t=1684147181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet your past self</h2>If you could go back in time and see your younger self, what would you have said to her? In the midst of chaos, the grown-up protagonist has met her past self. The two must work together to escape this time space<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility Settings</h2>Blind players can also play \"Red&Black\"! ! !<br>Through the game's accessibility settings, blin can also enjoy the fun of solving puzzles and action games.<br>This mode needs to start NVDA or call the NVDA interface for experience.",
